{"tid":994410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港coser賣淫 $6000有2Q","createTime":"2019-01-24T16:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T14:13:53.000Z","uid":199590,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"31dbe0b2d15e6041ad0df8a4530c40ed36b19966","tid":994410,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:22:13.000Z","msg":"櫻姬是香港知名Coser，常常會分享福利照給粉絲，臉書專頁擁有近30萬人點讚，不過日前她卻遭爆使用小號IG賣淫，與「買家」透過傳訊息的方式議價，只見兩人在5000港幣到7000港幣之間討論，最終決定為「6000/2hrs/2q」，代表2小時6000港幣，2次性服務。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGehdWt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGehdWt.jpg&h=f5354e16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POQL7gu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOQL7gu.jpg&h=c5594c48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在議價過程被曝光後，櫻姬將小號進行大清洗，原本的4千多追蹤被她刪到只剩2千多追蹤，還換大頭貼的圖片並更改帳號名稱，不過新大頭照與其他資訊仍看得出是她本人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OejtkBy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOejtkBy.jpg&h=b7ad6537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DpGn9uU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpGn9uU.jpg&h=c212813d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8f3bd011706e06252c3eaff0ba3c72d6b0bb524","tid":994410,"uid":1139,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b776c8149d7968d8c59fedb68eb421e35f1aa449","tid":994410,"uid":81518,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:24:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b1d3c1d8d24f6c4ccdaedacca9c1bf4d5a3e380","tid":994410,"uid":1675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:25:00.000Z","msg":"之前好似同個有老婆嘅呀叔一齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2051ca1358ca94d9f27a6299c0a570c837c1e58","tid":994410,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:25:09.